Package cscie97.asn4.ecommerce.csv

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CollectionImporter
    Provides a single public method for handling the creation of new Collections, adding Content to StaticCollections, defining the ContentSearch criteria for DynamicCollections, and lastly, for searching over these newly created Collections.
    ContentImporter
    Provides public static methods for supplying CSV files to load Country, Device, and Content items (which may be one of Application, Ringtone, or Wallpaper depending on the content type) into the Product catalog.
    Importer
    Abstract parent class of all other CSV loading and query implementing child classes.
    SearchEngine
    Provides public static methods for querying the ProductAPI for Content items.
